text: "Gold on the Ceiling" is a 2012 song by The Black Keys and is the third single from their seventh studio album El Camino. It went to number 57 in the United Kingdom, number 54 in Scotland, number 94 in the United States, number 51 in Canada, number 45 in Ireland and number 34 in Australia. ==References== Category:2012 songs Category:Garage rock songs Category:Glam rock songs Category:Blues rock songs Category:The Black Keys songs
title: Gold on the Ceiling
